title: She's the One 2013 WEBRip
description:
She's the One is a 2013 Filipino romantic-comedy film directed by Mae Cruz and stars Bea Alonzo, Dingdong Dantes and Enrique Gil. It is produced by Star Cinema for its 20th Anniversary presentation

A morning show host suddenly realizes what he really wants when his best friend turns out to be the subject of a romantic viral video that captures the attention of the whole nation.
